{"tid":642993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共威脅大　無國界記者工作重心移亞洲","createTime":"2018-04-26T07:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T07:44:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55d53776b3806b0ab1e4c2d011410af44393fb87","tid":642993,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:43:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180426/20373205?_ga=2.137398192.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373205%3F_ga%3D2.137398192.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=auvoVgDLv9QaieyI29Z%2BU2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=659bad70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373205%3F_ga%3D2.137398192.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=86d0d4c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180426/20373205?_ga=2.137398192.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月26日 <br />\n<br />\n中共威脅大　無國界記者工作重心移亞洲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/26cx4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2F26cx4p.jpg&h=72478b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■無國界記者在巴黎的土耳其大使館外抗議該國拘留記者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n無國界記者始建於1985年，是一個致力保護記者免受迫害、並推進新聞自由的政治性國際非政府組織。他們每年都會根據全球各地的新聞自由狀況，包括新聞自由是否獲尊重及傳媒運作環境等因素，發放「世界新聞自由指數」。<br />\n<br />\n無國界記者在2005年獲歐洲議會授予自由精神薩哈羅夫獎，他們曾打算在香港設立第一個亞洲辦事機構，但後來認為「香港難以保障」，故最終在去年將辦事處設在台北。他們明言，全世界言論與資訊自由最大的威脅來源之一是中國政府，故將工作重心移向亞洲。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n美跌兩名　多國學特以「假新聞」壓抑傳媒<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n深圳推人臉辨識系統　捉衝紅燈市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美跌兩名　多國學特以「假新聞」壓抑傳媒<br />\n<br />\n習治下肆意扣查傳媒人中國新聞自由排尾五"},{"pid":"614c16a934df7c16f9672b7f44f83ef06bf2a9a3","tid":642993,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/154431_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F154431_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=fbf035c6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}